{"id":118,"parent_id":95,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":118,"title":"Acts 23","subtitle":"","short_title":"Acts","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 23"],[".studySummary",["i","Paul is smitten at Ananias’s order—The Lord again appears to Paul—Forty Jews plot his death—He is delivered over to Felix."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.1","order":"03.07.023.14381"},["b","1"],"And Paul, earnestly beholding the council, said, Men",["i","and"],"brethren, I have lived in all good",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"conscience"],"before God until this day."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.2","order":"03.07.023.14382"},["b","2"],"And the high priest",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Ananias"],"commanded them that stood by him to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"smite"],"him on the mouth."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.3","order":"03.07.023.14383"},["b","3"],"Then said Paul unto him, God shall smite thee,",["i","thou"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"whited"],"wall: for sittest thou to judge me after the law, and commandest me to be smitten contrary to the law?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.4","order":"03.07.023.14384"},["b","4"],"And they that stood by said,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Revilest"],"thou God’s high priest?"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.5","order":"03.07.023.14385"},["b","5"],"Then said Paul, I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"wist"],"not, brethren, that he was the high priest: for it is written, Thou shalt not speak evil of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"ruler"],"of thy people."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.6","order":"03.07.023.14386"},["b","6"],"But when Paul perceived that the one part were Sadducees, and the other Pharisees, he cried out in the council, Men",["i","and"],"brethren, I am a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Pharisee"],", the son of a Pharisee: of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"hope"],"and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"resurrection"],"of the dead I am called in question."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.7","order":"03.07.023.14387"},["b","7"],"And when he had so said, there arose a dissension between the Pharisees and the Sadducees: and the multitude was divided."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.8","order":"03.07.023.14388"},["b","8"],"For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Sadducees"],"say that there is no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"resurrection"],", neither angel, nor spirit: but the Pharisees confess both."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.9","order":"03.07.023.14389"},["b","9"],"And there arose a great cry: and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"scribes"],["i","that were"],"of the Pharisees’ part arose, and strove, saying, We find no evil in this man: but if a spirit or an",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"angel"],"hath spoken to him, let us not",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"fight"],"against God."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.10","order":"03.07.023.14390"},["b","10"],"And when there arose a great dissension, the chief captain, fearing lest Paul should have been pulled in pieces of them, commanded the soldiers to go down, and to take him by force from among them, and to bring",["i","him"],"into the castle."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.11","order":"03.07.023.14391"},["b","11"],"And the night following the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Lord"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"stood"],"by him, and said, Be of good",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"cheer"],", Paul: for as thou hast testified of me in Jerusalem, so must thou bear witness also at",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"Rome"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.12","order":"03.07.023.14392"},["b","12"],"And when it was day, certain of the Jews banded together, and bound themselves under a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"curse"],", saying that they would neither eat nor drink till they had",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"killed"],"Paul."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.13","order":"03.07.023.14393"},["b","13"],"And they were more than forty which had made this",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"conspiracy"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.14","order":"03.07.023.14394"},["b","14"],"And they came to the chief priests and elders, and said, We have bound ourselves under a great curse, that we will eat nothing until we have slain Paul."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.15","order":"03.07.023.14395"},["b","15"],"Now therefore ye with the council signify to the chief captain that he bring him down unto you to morrow, as though ye would inquire something more perfectly concerning him: and we,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"or"],"ever he come near, are ready to kill him."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.16","order":"03.07.023.14396"},["b","16"],"And when Paul’s sister’s son heard of their lying in wait, he went and entered into the castle, and told Paul."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.17","order":"03.07.023.14397"},["b","17"],"Then Paul called one of the centurions unto",["i","him,"],"and said, Bring this young man unto the chief captain: for he hath a certain thing to tell him."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.18","order":"03.07.023.14398"},["b","18"],"So he took him, and brought",["i","him"],"to the chief captain, and said, Paul the prisoner called me unto",["i","him,"],"and prayed me to bring this young man unto thee, who hath something to say unto thee."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.19","order":"03.07.023.14399"},["b","19"],"Then the chief captain took him by the hand, and went",["i","with him"],"aside privately, and asked",["i","him,"],"What is that thou hast to tell me?"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.20","order":"03.07.023.14400"},["b","20"],"And he said, The Jews have agreed to desire thee that thou wouldest bring down Paul to morrow into the council, as though they would inquire somewhat of him more perfectly."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.21","order":"03.07.023.14401"},["b","21"],"But do not thou yield unto them: for there lie in wait for him of them more than forty men, which have bound themselves with an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"oath"],", that they will neither eat nor drink till they have killed him: and now are they ready, looking for a promise from thee."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.22","order":"03.07.023.14402"},["b","22"],"So the chief captain",["i","then"],"let the young man depart, and charged",["i","him, See thou"],"tell no man that thou hast shewed these things to me."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.23","order":"03.07.023.14403"},["b","23"],"And he called unto",["i","him"],"two centurions, saying, Make ready two hundred soldiers to go to Cæsarea, and horsemen threescore and ten, and spearmen two hundred, at the third hour of the night;"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.24","order":"03.07.023.14404"},["b","24"],"And provide",["i","them"],"beasts, that they may set Paul on, and bring",["i","him"],"safe unto Felix the governor."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.25","order":"03.07.023.14405"},["b","25"],"And he wrote a letter after this manner:"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.26","order":"03.07.023.14406"},["b","26"],"Claudius",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"Lysias"],"unto the most excellent governor Felix",["i","sendeth"],"greeting."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.27","order":"03.07.023.14407"},["b","27"],"This man was taken of the Jews, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"should"],"have been killed of them: then came I with an",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"army"],", and rescued him, having understood that he was a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_27c"},"Roman"],"."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.28","order":"03.07.023.14408"},["b","28"],"And when I would have known the cause wherefore they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"accused"],"him, I brought him forth into their council:"],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.29","order":"03.07.023.14409"},["b","29"],"Whom I perceived to be accused of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"questions"],"of their law, but to have nothing laid to his charge worthy of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_29b"},"death"],"or of bonds."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.30","order":"03.07.023.14410"},["b","30"],"And when it was told me how that the Jews laid wait for the man, I sent",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"straightway"],"to thee, and gave commandment to his accusers also to say before thee what",["i","they had"],"against him. Farewell."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.31","order":"03.07.023.14411"},["b","31"],"Then the soldiers, as it was commanded them, took Paul, and brought",["i","him"],"by night to Antipatris."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.32","order":"03.07.023.14412"},["b","32"],"On the morrow they left the horsemen to go with him, and returned to the castle:"],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.33","order":"03.07.023.14413"},["b","33"],"Who, when they came to Cæsarea, and delivered the epistle to the governor, presented Paul also before him."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.34","order":"03.07.023.14414"},["b","34"],"And when the governor had read",["i","the letter,"],"he asked of what province he was. And when he understood that",["i","he was"],"of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"Cilicia"],";"],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.35","order":"03.07.023.14415"},["b","35"],"I will hear thee, said he, when thine accusers are also come. And he commanded him to be kept in Herod’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"judgment hall"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.1a","order":"03.07.023.14416"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conscience"},"TG Conscience"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.2a","order":"03.07.023.14418"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/24.1"},"Acts 24:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.2b","order":"03.07.023.14420"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/18.22.20-23"},"John 18:22 (20–23)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.3a","order":"03.07.023.14422"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/5.9.9-10"},"Ps. 5:9 (9–10)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/23.27"},"Matt. 23:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/11.44"},"Luke 11:44"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.4a","order":"03.07.023.14424"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reviling"},"TG Reviling"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.5a","order":"03.07.023.14426"},["b","5a"],["span.small","OR"],"knew."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.5b","order":"03.07.023.14428"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/citizenship"},"TG Citizenship"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.6a","order":"03.07.023.14430"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.5"},"Acts 26:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/philip/3.5"},"Philip. 3:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.6b","order":"03.07.023.14432"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/28.20"},"Acts 28:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.6c","order":"03.07.023.14434"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/24.21"},"Acts 24:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.8a","order":"03.07.023.14436"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.23"},"Matt. 22:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.8b","order":"03.07.023.14438"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.2"},"Acts 4:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.9a","order":"03.07.023.14440"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scribe"},"TG Scribe"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.9b","order":"03.07.023.14442"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.8.6-10"},"Acts 22:8 (6–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.9c","order":"03.07.023.14444"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/5.39.34-40"},"Acts 5:39 (34–40)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.11a","order":"03.07.023.14446"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vision"},"TG Vision"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.11b","order":"03.07.023.14448"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-appearances-postmortal"},"TG Jesus Christ, Appearances, Postmortal"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.11c","order":"03.07.023.14450"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/10.4.2-5"},"Hel. 10:4 (2–5)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.7.1-7"},"D&C 121:7 (1–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.11d","order":"03.07.023.14452"},["b","11d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/19.21"},"Acts 19:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.12a","order":"03.07.023.14454"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"TG Curse"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.12b","order":"03.07.023.14456"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/25.3.2-3"},"Acts 25:3 (2–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/49.27.26-27"},"Alma 49:27 (26–27)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/51.9"},"51:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.13a","order":"03.07.023.14458"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conspiracy"},"TG Conspiracy"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.15a","order":"03.07.023.14460"},["b","15a"],["span.small","OR"],"before he gets here."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.21a","order":"03.07.023.14462"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vow"},"TG Vow"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.26a","order":"03.07.023.14464"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.28"},"Acts 22:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/24.22"},"24:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.27a","order":"03.07.023.14466"},["b","27a"],["span.small","JST"],"Acts 23:27 …",["i","would"],"…"],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.27b","order":"03.07.023.14468"},["b","27b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.32"},"Acts 21:32"],"."],["div",{"id":"27c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.27c","order":"03.07.023.14470"},["b","27c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.25"},"Acts 22:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.28a","order":"03.07.023.14472"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.30"},"Acts 22:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.29a","order":"03.07.023.14474"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.15.12-17"},"Acts 18:15 (12–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"29b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.29b","order":"03.07.023.14476"},["b","29b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/25.25"},"Acts 25:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.30a","order":"03.07.023.14478"},["b","30a"],["span.small","GR"],"immediately."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.34a","order":"03.07.023.14480"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.39"},"Acts 21:39"],"."],["div",{"id":"35a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.35a","order":"03.07.023.14482"},["b","35a"],["span.small","GR"],["i","praetorium"],"(the governor’s headquarters)."]]}
